TEXT -4056 984 Left 2 !* SUBCKT Definition:  1=D  2=G  3=S\n**********************************************************************\n.SUBCKT CSD17308Q3  1 2 3\n.PARAM  ptrc1   3.10e-3  \n.PARAM  ptrc2   9.5e-6\n.PARAM  pwidthP 0.6120192\n.PARAM  pwidth  {pwidthP*1e6}\n.PARAM  perimP  {2.1*pwidthP}\n.PARAM  perim   {perimP*1e6}\n*pkgL = logical value:  0 for Si Die ONLY;  1 for packaged part.\n.PARAM  pkgL    1.0\nM1   10 11 12 12  NMOS W={pwidthP} L=0.5u  PD={perimP}  PS={perimP}\nDBD   8  7         DBD\nRDB   8  7   1e10\nCGD0  5  7              {pkgL*1E-12 + 1e-14}\nCGS0  5  8                {pkgL*2e-12 + 1e-14}\nCDS0 10 12                {pkgL*5e-12 + 1e-14}\nM2   12 11 12 20  PMOSd W={pwidthP} L=0.103u  PD={perimP}  PS={perimP}\nDDx  20 10   DDx\nDDG  14  5   DD\nDGD  14 10   DD\n* Note:  gate oxide capacitance included in NMOS below\nCGS   5 13            72E-12\nRGS  13  8              190\nLGG   2  5                 {pkgL*0.95e-9 + 0.1e-9}\nRGG   5 11             {pkgL*0.25 + 0.8}\nRSB  12  9   RTEMP 0.90E-3\nRSS   9  8       0.04e-3\nRSP   8  6             {pkgL*0.50e-3 + 0.02e-3}\nLSS   6  3            {pkgL*0.51E-9 + 0.02e-9}\nRSL   6  3   2.5\nRDP   4  7          {pkgL*0.65e-3 + 0.05e-3}\nRDD   7 10            RTEMP 3.69e-3\nLDD   1  4       0.05E-9\n******************************************************************* \n.MODEL  NMOS   NMOS (    LEVEL  = 7             Version = 3.2\n+ TNOM   = 27            LINT   = 0.055e-6      CAPMOD = 2\n+ TOX    = 1.75e-8       NCH    = 1.598e17      NSUB   = 1.0e16\n+ AGS    = 0.0           PVAG   = 0.2\n+ A0     = 1.10          A1     = 0.0           A2     = 0.9\n+ UA     = 1.30e-9       UB     = 3.0e-18       VBM    = -5.0\n+ UA1    = 2.4e-9        UB1    = -3.5e-18      UTE    = -1.50\n+ KT1    = -0.64         KT2    = 0.022         KT1L   = 1.0e-12\n+ DVT0   = 2.5           DVT1   = 0.62              DVT2   = -0.033\n+ ETA0   = 0.045         ETAB   = -0.07         XJ     = 4e-7\n+ PDIBLC1= 0.08          PDIBLC2= 0.025         NLX    = 1.78e-7\n+ PSCBE1 = 6.0e8         PSCBE2 = 1e-7          PCLM   = 1.3\n+ VOFF   = -0.235        NFACTOR= 1.4           JS     = 0\n+ DROUT  = 1.10          DSUB   = 1.3           DELTA  = 0.01\n+ CJ     = 1e-18         CJSW   = 1e-18         CF     = 0\n+ CGSO   = 161e-12       CGDO   = 21e-12        CGBO   = 0    )\n******************************************************************* \n.MODEL  PMOSd   PMOS (   LEVEL  = 1\n+ TNOM   = 27            VTO    = -0.3                 IS     = 6.0e-14\n+ TOX    = 1.75e-8       NSUB   = 2e18\n+ CJ     = 1e-18         CJSW   = 1e-18\n+ CGSO   = 1e-18         CGDO   = 1e-18         CGBO   = 1e-18 )\n******************************************************************* \n.MODEL DBD D (CJO=1100e-12 VJ=1.0 M=0.525 FC=0.5 TT=2e-09 TNOM=27\n+ IS=1.1e-12 N=1.01 RS=3.0e-3 TRS1=3.3e-3 XTI=2.8 BV=33)\n.MODEL DDx D (CJO=20e-12 VJ=0.40 M=0.50 IS=1e-12 RS=0.1 TNOM=27)\n.MODEL DD  D (CJO=205e-12 VJ=0.40 M=0.838 IS=1e-13 RS=1 TNOM=27 BV=31)\n******************************************************************* \n.MODEL RTEMP RES (TC1={ptrc1} TC2={ptrc2})\n*******************************************************************\n.ENDS CSD17308Q3\n*$
